        "TileImage": "$($repository 3ed1c7e6-7707-48b4-a0f0-b933bc851fdb).Image",
        "Description": "Step into a world of high-stakes assasination as you take on targets that are as challenging as a game of hide-and-seek with a toddler. The contestants in this level are a real piece of work. It&apos;s almost like they got their training from a &quot;How Not to Be a Hitman&quot; handbook. From leaving trails of breadcrumbs leading directly to their hideouts to mistaking the tranquilizer for the lethal poison, it&apos;s a wonder they made it this far in the business.",
